{"id":455741,"date":[{"year":1964,"month":6,"day":1}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"368","ytitle":"","mtitle":"里弄孩子办的报","ftitle":"","authors":["任溶溶"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"任溶溶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我每一次走进弄堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总要抬头望一望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们里弄里的孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们把报办在墙头上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我屈指头算了一下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天要看五份报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国内外的重大事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我可以说都知道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不过我对这一份报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是非常有兴趣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为上面写的事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都出在我里弄里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才知道几号那家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住着一位老伯伯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他过去的日子很苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今是位先进工作者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才知道在我周围，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先进人物多又多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我过去看见他们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一点儿也不晓得。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才知道小朋友们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做了不少好事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好事多得没法逐个表扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干脆列成了统计表。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小朋友们一面编报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面也是自己受教育。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这张报也教育了我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它给了我许多东西。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们的编辑会议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我两年前参加过；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我在看报时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个编辑委员站到我身旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我对他说编得挺好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他笑了笑对我说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“有人接上我的班啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的儿子是一个。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的家里还有记者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这我可是没想到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我得好好努力一下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许有天会上报。"}]}